@database PopimageClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Popimage Class"


Popimage class    @{"Index" link "Classes"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Popimage class is used to adjust an image spec.

  Set Draggable to 1 to do drag and drop beetween two
  Popimage objects (using Auto in DandD()).

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}POSpec@{fg text}
  S ISGN
  If you know what you are doing, you know what it is.

  @{fg shine}POTitle@{fg text}
  S I
  The title of the pop-up window.

  @{fg shine}POType@{fg text}
  M I
  A number or one of:
  o All
  o Image
  o Background
  o Pen

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

@EndNode

